<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="59600000t" end="68300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">这里是？</p>
<p begin="71500000t" end="88900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">学园的医务室</p>
<p begin="99800000t" end="108900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">这样啊</p>
<p begin="122800000t" end="135900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">发生了什么事</p>
<p begin="144700000t" end="171700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">伊莉娜被拐走了</p>
<p begin="179600000t" end="191600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">谁干的</p>
<p begin="202500000t" end="231500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">狂龙王 艾尔莎德</p>
<p begin="397700000t" end="430500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">足以融化孤独的呼声</p>
<p begin="430500000t" end="468800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">究竟来自于何人？</p>
<p begin="474900000t" end="519100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">向往着温暖 我出发了。</p>
<p begin="519100000t" end="536500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">再来，再来，再来！</p>
<p begin="541300000t" end="558300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">咏唱 交个朋友</p>
<p begin="558300000t" end="574700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">解除 扑克脸</p>
<p begin="574700000t" end="606100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">平起平坐的坦诚交谈</p>
<p begin="607700000t" end="625300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">打破墙壁吧 用转移魔法</p>
<p begin="625300000t" end="641300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">瞬间便融洽相处</p>
<p begin="641300000t" end="657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">共鸣之和谐 打破孤独</p>
<p begin="657400000t" end="671100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">精准无比 太完美了吧？</p>
<p begin="671100000t" end="734600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">沉默寡言的挑战者 迈出第一步</p>
<p begin="734600000t" end="788500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">生涩的自己也要抱紧</p>
<p begin="792400000t" end="826500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">一起开始尝试！就是现在 尝试！</p>
<p begin="829800000t" end="867900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">向奇迹发起挑战吧</p>
<p begin="867900000t" end="908200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">将无敌的心情连结到底</p>
<p begin="908200000t" end="925200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">放马过来 放马过来</p>
<p begin="925200000t" end="959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">鼓足干劲 尝试！发展超乎想像</p>
<p begin="961500000t" end="993300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">点燃勇气</p>
<p begin="993300000t" end="1032800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">即使现在相隔遥远</p>
<p begin="1032800000t" end="1067200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">有朝一日 也必定能相互理解</p>
<p begin="1067200000t" end="1082900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">做我的朋友！！！</p>
<p begin="1082900000t" end="1136800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">哔哩哔哩译制<br />Translated by bilibili</p>
<p begin="1151600000t" end="1173800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">狂龙王 艾尔莎德？</p>
<p begin="1181900000t" end="1212200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">那个几千年前险些毁灭世界的狂龙王？</p>
<p begin="1215400000t" end="1244600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">那不是比肩魔族和邪神的怪物吗</p>
<p begin="1248300000t" end="1279400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">这么强的怪物 为什么要拐走伊莉娜同学</p>
<p begin="1283000000t" end="1302700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">一定是因为…</p>
<p begin="1302700000t" end="1322100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">这根本不重要吧</p>
<p begin="1334600000t" end="1352800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">把伊莉娜小姐救回来</p>
<p begin="1355800000t" end="1389700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">无论对手是谁 该考虑的问题只有这一个</p>
<p begin="1393400000t" end="1425900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">说得太轻巧了 就算是你…</p>
<p begin="1425900000t" end="1457400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">我的字典里没有不可能这个词</p>
<p begin="1481900000t" end="1500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">我儿子就是不一样</p>
<p begin="1503100000t" end="1515600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">是吧 维斯</p>
<p begin="1559900000t" end="1576900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">那我有个建议</p>
<p begin="1609500000t" end="1618800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">这里是？</p>
<p begin="1623100000t" end="1637100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">王家的宝物库</p>
<p begin="1642000000t" end="1662000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">现在什么都别问 宝物拿去用吧</p>
<p begin="1667300000t" end="1683700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">全部托付给你了</p>
<p begin="1686600000t" end="1704200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">非常感谢</p>
<p begin="1725000000t" end="1736500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">这样好吗</p>
<p begin="1736500000t" end="1761300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">这次就只能依靠他了</p>
<p begin="1761300000t" end="1775300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">我不是这意思</p>
<p begin="1775300000t" end="1804100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">不告诉他你们的身世吗</p>
<p begin="1814700000t" end="1844100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">伊莉娜在遇见亚德前</p>
<p begin="1847300000t" end="1867700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">一直闭门不出</p>
<p begin="1876400000t" end="1913600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">在当时的她看来 别人都是恐惧的对象</p>
<p begin="1924600000t" end="1956300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">我们的秘密不可能永远瞒下去</p>
<p begin="1956300000t" end="1980000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">她出于本能意识到了这一点</p>
<p begin="1986700000t" end="2000900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">而现在也一样</p>
<p begin="2013900000t" end="2044400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">自从遇见亚德后 伊莉娜就改变了</p>
<p begin="2049300000t" end="2060400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">不过 那也是因为…</p>
<p begin="2066100000t" end="2102800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">他不知道我们一族的真相</p>
<p begin="2111800000t" end="2147500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">要我向亚德坦白真相 我办不到</p>
<p begin="2157100000t" end="2179000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">他是伊莉娜好不容易才找到的朋友</p>
<p begin="2182600000t" end="2200200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">我怎么能夺走他</p>
<p begin="2267500000t" end="2301800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">你真的愿意跟我这种人做朋友吗</p>
<p begin="2309500000t" end="2323400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">发生什么事都愿意吗</p>
<p begin="2323400000t" end="2352100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">绝对不会背叛我 不会讨厌我吗</p>
<p begin="2361100000t" end="2384100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我向魔王巴尔巴托斯发誓</p>
<p begin="2398000000t" end="2418700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">向魔王巴尔巴托斯发誓…</p>
<p begin="2426400000t" end="2460300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">今后还请多多指教 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="2479000000t" end="2496500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我想先问你一下</p>
<p begin="2499600000t" end="2509000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">问什么</p>
<p begin="2515000000t" end="2541200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">告诉我你的真实身份吧</p>
<p begin="2556700000t" end="2583700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我…其实是…</p>
<p begin="2704800000t" end="2713700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">亚德？</p>
<p begin="2763200000t" end="2772400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">亚德？</p>
<p begin="2776800000t" end="2803400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">亚德</p>
<p begin="2831000000t" end="2840200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">是梦吗</p>
<p begin="2917300000t" end="2930700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">这是什么</p>
<p begin="2942100000t" end="2963100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">哟 伊莉娜同学</p>
<p begin="2971500000t" end="2992700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">感觉怎样啊</p>
<p begin="2992700000t" end="3022400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">我想赶紧开始仪式</p>
<p begin="3027300000t" end="3056700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">到底是怎么回事 为什么要抓我</p>
<p begin="3061000000t" end="3091600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">真讨厌 明知故问</p>
<p begin="3094600000t" end="3120200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">我想要的是「你们一族」的血</p>
<p begin="3143100000t" end="3167400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">你怎么知道我们的秘密</p>
<p begin="3176300000t" end="3204300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">你猜是为什么呢</p>
<p begin="3210700000t" end="3239600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">这不重要 你能看见吧</p>
<p begin="3269000000t" end="3299200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">那东西叫「混沌的弃儿」</p>
<p begin="3304700000t" end="3327900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">魔王巴尔巴托斯曾消灭了诸多邪神</p>
<p begin="3327900000t" end="3369100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">这是用他们的肉块创造出的东西</p>
<p begin="3377000000t" end="3442200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">将这拥有邪神肉体的怪物和你一并献祭</p>
<p begin="3442200000t" end="3490200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">以召唤被封印在异空间的一位邪神</p>
<p begin="3515400000t" end="3528200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">为什么要这样做</p>
<p begin="3534600000t" end="3555200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">那还不简单吗</p>
<p begin="3555200000t" end="3578400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">就知道说什么爱啊 牵绊啊 友情啊</p>
<p begin="3578400000t" end="3618400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">我想毁了这沉浸在温吞感情中的世界啊</p>
<p begin="3618400000t" end="3652300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">如此让人不悦的世界 灭亡了才好</p>
<p begin="3694200000t" end="3746900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我从几千年前兴风作浪时起 行动理念就只有这一个</p>
<p begin="3752000000t" end="3769700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">休想得逞</p>
<p begin="3772500000t" end="3782400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">亚德会…</p>
<p begin="3787900000t" end="3808800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">亚德绝对会赶来的</p>
<p begin="3812200000t" end="3831100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">真的吗</p>
<p begin="3835500000t" end="3872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">他确实拥有远超常人的强大实力</p>
<p begin="3872400000t" end="3916400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">可不管他再强 终究是人类啊</p>
<p begin="3920500000t" end="3932300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">那又怎么了</p>
<p begin="3935800000t" end="3953300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">假设一下</p>
<p begin="3959700000t" end="4000600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">如果他知道了你的秘密 会怎样呢</p>
<p begin="4011100000t" end="4056500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">他如果知道了真相 就会讨厌你</p>
<p begin="4056500000t" end="4084300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">就会鄙视你 把你当成怪物</p>
<p begin="4231900000t" end="4250100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">真是苦了你了</p>
<p begin="4254900000t" end="4275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那就开始仪式吧</p>
<p begin="4409900000t" end="4420400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">亚德同学</p>
<p begin="4447300000t" end="4479900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">你要去救伊莉娜小姐对吧</p>
<p begin="4486000000t" end="4527600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">嗯 不过这次伴随着不小的风险</p>
<p begin="4531600000t" end="4549800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">所以我不能带你一起去</p>
<p begin="4553300000t" end="4601300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">亚德同学 在我看来 是你向我传授了力量</p>
<p begin="4605600000t" end="4637700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我才有了自信 做出了改变</p>
<p begin="4648400000t" end="4676200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">但是 我没能交到朋友</p>
<p begin="4685000000t" end="4696900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">金妮小姐</p>
<p begin="4696900000t" end="4732500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我原以为这一辈子都不会变了</p>
<p begin="4736100000t" end="4767000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">我注定要永远孤单 已经放弃了</p>
<p begin="4775600000t" end="4801000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">但是 伊莉娜小姐她…</p>
<p begin="4827300000t" end="4873500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">不许伤害我的朋友</p>
<p begin="4880200000t" end="4914500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">竟然把我这种人当成了朋友</p>
<p begin="4919000000t" end="4928700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">所以</p>
<p begin="4962900000t" end="4989600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">应该能在晚餐时间前赶回来</p>
<p begin="5006000000t" end="5046600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">金妮小姐 你就做好美味的晚饭等我们回来吧</p>
<p begin="5051400000t" end="5085300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">到时候伊莉娜小姐肯定饿坏了</p>
<p begin="5113600000t" end="5130200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">那我出发了</p>
<p begin="5165300000t" end="5203300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">对了 你刚才说自己交不到朋友</p>
<p begin="5207400000t" end="5223590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">其实不只是伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="5223590000t" end="5257800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我也把你当朋友的哦</p>
<p begin="5261300000t" end="5272800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">亚德同学</p>
<p begin="5276800000t" end="5293700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">等伊莉娜小姐回来了</p>
<p begin="5297900000t" end="5328700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">再一起干傻事 一起欢笑吧</p>
<p begin="5351400000t" end="5359400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">好</p>
<p begin="5465500000t" end="5490500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不要 住手 别过来…</p>
<p begin="5493900000t" end="5514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">别过来</p>
<p begin="5605100000t" end="5629400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">两个怪物多般配啊</p>
<p begin="5976700000t" end="5986800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">亚德</p>
<p begin="5992600000t" end="6016900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">你来了 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="6035400000t" end="6065400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">各位蝼蚁 你们好</p>
<p begin="6105300000t" end="6130100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">你们这次胆子挺大啊</p>
<p begin="6134700000t" end="6163800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我一只都不会放过的</p>
<p begin="6169600000t" end="6182600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">准备受死吧</p>
<p begin="6221700000t" end="6232000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">别慌</p>
<p begin="6258200000t" end="6275400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">什么 九重施法</p>
<p begin="6383700000t" end="6417400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">伊莉娜小姐 抱歉 我来晚了</p>
<p begin="6470700000t" end="6488700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">亚德</p>
<p begin="6497300000t" end="6515900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">我好怕</p>
<p begin="6585600000t" end="6601600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">有两下子啊</p>
<p begin="6632900000t" end="6658600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">好久没有这种感觉了</p>
<p begin="6658600000t" end="6682100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">都快疯了</p>
<p begin="6785400000t" end="6798500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">放心</p>
<p begin="6802900000t" end="6841000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">这种水平的蜥蜴 根本不是我的对手</p>
<p begin="6845600000t" end="6865100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">你还真能秀啊</p>
<p begin="6868200000t" end="6897300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">你就这么喜欢那怪物吗</p>
<p begin="6901300000t" end="6911000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">怪物？</p>
<p begin="6923100000t" end="6963900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">她可没你想像中那么美丽</p>
<p begin="6967200000t" end="6993600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">别看她现在叫奥尔海德</p>
<p begin="6993600000t" end="7012700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">那只是假名罢了</p>
<p begin="7012700000t" end="7033100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">住口 不要说出来</p>
<p begin="7036000000t" end="7084000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">她真正的名字是拉维尔 是真正的王族</p>
<p begin="7089300000t" end="7115600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">然后 她呢</p>
<p begin="7145200000t" end="7174100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">其实继承了「邪神」的血脉哦</p>
<p begin="7220100000t" end="7256400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">在这世界上 信奉魔王的宗教占据着主导地位</p>
<p begin="7260300000t" end="7289600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">「邪神」无一不是人们厌恶的对象</p>
<p begin="7300200000t" end="7339100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">如果我们王族继承了邪神血脉这事传出去</p>
<p begin="7339100000t" end="7357300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">国家很可能被颠覆</p>
<p begin="7369800000t" end="7409200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">所以要利用替身 间接统治…</p>
<p begin="7425800000t" end="7450500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">嗯 不过正因如此</p>
<p begin="7454500000t" end="7490000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我只能逼迫女儿彻底隐瞒自己的身份</p>
<p begin="7497100000t" end="7523300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">毕竟亚德还不知道</p>
<p begin="7523300000t" end="7550900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">你们才是这国家「真正的王族」</p>
<p begin="7561500000t" end="7574800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">这或许会害我女儿…</p>
<p begin="7582800000t" end="7626400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">失去这辈子交到的第一个朋友</p>
<p begin="7665400000t" end="7692200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">话先说清楚 这都是真的</p>
<p begin="7692200000t" end="7724000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">所以拉斯·阿勒·古尔才会打她的主意</p>
<p begin="7728900000t" end="7750300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">这根本不重要</p>
<p begin="7758400000t" end="7770700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">你说什么</p>
<p begin="7774300000t" end="7823700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">不管她是继承了邪神血脉 还是邪神本神 我都不在乎</p>
<p begin="7828300000t" end="7878800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">重要的是 她比任何人都善良 比任何人都勇敢</p>
<p begin="7878800000t" end="7902300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">她是个值得尊敬与喜爱的人</p>
<p begin="7910000000t" end="7935700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">在我这种人眼里 她真的太耀眼了</p>
<p begin="7939500000t" end="7961100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">简直像太阳一样伟大</p>
<p begin="7965000000t" end="8019200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">你就用简简单单的一句怪物歧视她</p>
<p begin="8024800000t" end="8045000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">我绝饶不了你</p>
<p begin="8061300000t" end="8098100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">我越来越想看你绝望的表情了</p>
<p begin="8176400000t" end="8218700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">不对劲 他好像并没有发动防御魔法</p>
<p begin="8218700000t" end="8236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">也就是说 是那把枪搞的鬼吗</p>
<p begin="8239400000t" end="8286000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">它拥有能让雷属性攻击魔法无效化的效果</p>
<p begin="8293900000t" end="8335800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">你以为这点雕虫小技就能让我绝望吗</p>
<p begin="8369100000t" end="8398200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">艾尔莎德小姐 你脚下没设防哦</p>
<p begin="8499300000t" end="8547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">你的战斗方式充斥着绝对强者才有的缺点</p>
<p begin="8550200000t" end="8593000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">没经历过苦战的人 打法难免单一</p>
<p begin="8620600000t" end="8657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">在我看来 强者缺乏危机感</p>
<p begin="8665500000t" end="8678900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">你也一样</p>
<p begin="8678900000t" end="8714500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">都大难临头了 似乎仍然坚信自己不会死</p>
<p begin="8718300000t" end="8734300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">那又如何</p>
<p begin="8740000000t" end="8763500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我可以很负责地告诉你</p>
<p begin="8766900000t" end="8786600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">这世上无法消灭的存在</p>
<p begin="8792200000t" end="8812100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">根本不存在</p>
<p begin="8899600000t" end="8926600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">亚德 太好了</p>
<p begin="8926600000t" end="8953700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">你没受伤就好</p>
<p begin="8960200000t" end="8967500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">不</p>
<p begin="9018500000t" end="9050900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">亚德梅特奥…</p>
<p begin="9054300000t" end="9086800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">还没完 离结束还早着呢</p>
<p begin="9125700000t" end="9159700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">真受不了 纠缠不休的女人会招人厌的</p>
<p begin="9196300000t" end="9214900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">灰飞烟灭吧</p>
<p begin="9241200000t" end="9250700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="9254200000t" end="9286700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">我希望你不要看接下来的战斗</p>
<p begin="9286700000t" end="9295300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">亚德？</p>
<p begin="9303100000t" end="9325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">「那条路上遍布绝望」</p>
<p begin="9329100000t" end="9351900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">「那是可悲男人的人生写照」</p>
<p begin="9351900000t" end="9365700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">「其人孤独」</p>
<p begin="9365700000t" end="9379700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">「有人追随」</p>
<p begin="9379700000t" end="9404200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">「却无人伴他共求霸业」</p>
<p begin="9407800000t" end="9429800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">「不为任何人理解」</p>
<p begin="9429800000t" end="9454500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">「惨遭所有人离弃」</p>
<p begin="9454500000t" end="9475700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">「唯一的朋友亦抛他而去」</p>
<p begin="9475700000t" end="9505800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">「他在疯狂和孤独的海洋中沉沦」</p>
<p begin="9523600000t" end="9560600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">绝望吧 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="9560600000t" end="9585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">「临终之际仍不得安宁」</p>
<p begin="9585000000t" end="9611700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">「只得心怀悲叹和绝望溺亡」</p>
<p begin="9624000000t" end="9637000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">「想必这就是」</p>
<p begin="9646400000t" end="9674100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">- 「孤独之王的故事…」<br />- 私人王国</p>
<p begin="9683600000t" end="9700800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">这…这是？</p>
<p begin="9720000000t" end="9758400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">威胁认定级别3级 限制解除15%</p>
<p begin="9777100000t" end="9792400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">防御活动开始</p>
<p begin="9936000000t" end="9949700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">那是什么…</p>
<p begin="9949700000t" end="9968800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">你究竟是什么人</p>
<p begin="9971700000t" end="9999100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">来支许久未跳的舞吧 莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="9999100000t" end="10010600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">遵命 我的王</p>
<p begin="10079700000t" end="10095400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">我只是一介村民</p>
<p begin="10114200000t" end="10135500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">在你的地盘陪你打好了</p>
<p begin="10135500000t" end="10149700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">跟上来 贱龙</p>
<p begin="10159600000t" end="10181500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">你要跟龙打空战吗</p>
<p begin="10181500000t" end="10212300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">如此傲慢 我要让你以死谢罪</p>
<p begin="10254800000t" end="10268790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">下方出现魔力反应</p>
<p begin="10271590000t" end="10300200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">0.2秒后 大概率形成魔法阵</p>
<p begin="10345600000t" end="10367600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">左侧 右侧出现高热反应</p>
<p begin="10371390000t" end="10404700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">若保持当前运动速度 将于3秒后被直接命中</p>
<p begin="10404700000t" end="10437200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">构建加速术式 回避后反击</p>
<p begin="10441690000t" end="10452000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">遵命 我的王</p>
<p begin="10495400000t" end="10525100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">莉迪娅 代号阿尔法 预备</p>
<p begin="10533800000t" end="10561400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">明白 「行刑者射线」准备发射</p>
<p begin="10573700000t" end="10588200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">准备完毕 可以发射</p>
<p begin="10613900000t" end="10634200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">太慢了太慢了 雕虫小技</p>
<p begin="10655700000t" end="10669700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">不足为惧</p>
<p begin="10674200000t" end="10707600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">你还是直接死在这会更幸福吧</p>
<p begin="10719200000t" end="10741900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">虽说伊莉娜同学已经算怪物了</p>
<p begin="10741900000t" end="10759100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">但你更是超乎常理</p>
<p begin="10778000000t" end="10807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">同类绝不可能做朋友</p>
<p begin="10814500000t" end="10850000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">恐怕她会畏惧你 毫不犹豫地背叛你吧</p>
<p begin="10892600000t" end="10925600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">这世上既不存在友情 也不存在爱情</p>
<p begin="10933300000t" end="10943000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">亚德…</p>
<p begin="10984200000t" end="11010300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">孤独地去死吧</p>
<p begin="11010300000t" end="11031000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">这才是你该有的死法</p>
<p begin="11035600000t" end="11054800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">亚德</p>
<p begin="11069100000t" end="11088800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">加油</p>
<p begin="11092500000t" end="11122800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">你可不能输给那种家伙啊</p>
<p begin="11147900000t" end="11167700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">你弄错了一点</p>
<p begin="11172100000t" end="11194100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">我已经不再是孤单一人了</p>
<p begin="11216900000t" end="11237500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">莉迪娅 阶段2 预备</p>
<p begin="11249000000t" end="11286000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">明白 勇魔附体 进入第二形态</p>
<p begin="11378900000t" end="11389900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">解析完毕</p>
<p begin="11400000000t" end="11421500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">执行魔法扫描</p>
<p begin="11491500000t" end="11523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">结束了 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="11574700000t" end="11595200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">到底…怎么回事…</p>
<p begin="11605900000t" end="11635900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">解析 理解 控制</p>
<p begin="11635900000t" end="11654100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">这才是我的本质</p>
<p begin="11660400000t" end="11686200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">我已经彻底理解你了</p>
<p begin="11686200000t" end="11710900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">不只是构成魔法的术式</p>
<p begin="11715200000t" end="11733300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">内心的本质也不例外</p>
<p begin="11737500000t" end="11746300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">啊？</p>
<p begin="11749800000t" end="11768100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">归根结底</p>
<p begin="11768100000t" end="11799800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">世界将孤独强加于你</p>
<p begin="11799800000t" end="11817200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">你只是厌恶了这种处境吧</p>
<p begin="11839200000t" end="11869000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">你这泄愤般的破坏行为</p>
<p begin="11869000000t" end="11891500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">竟敢牵连我的朋友 罪无可赦</p>
<p begin="11916800000t" end="11958900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">狂暴的龙王 与绝望一同死去吧</p>
<p begin="11964500000t" end="12002800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">这还是我第一次这么愤怒</p>
<p begin="12018000000t" end="12040400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">代号西格玛 预备</p>
<p begin="12045300000t" end="12053700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">明白</p>
<p begin="12057100000t" end="12077000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">「最后通牒·归零」准备发射</p>
<p begin="12111900000t" end="12154200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">魔力填充率 40% 50%…</p>
<p begin="12154200000t" end="12178300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">「埃尔西姆」「路法撒」「乌尔维斯」「亚兹拉」</p>
<p begin="12202600000t" end="12232200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">80% 90%</p>
<p begin="12245700000t" end="12287700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">填充率已到达100% 请指示</p>
<p begin="12287700000t" end="12301600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">无需多言</p>
<p begin="12304700000t" end="12322200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">最后通牒·归零</p>
<p begin="12346500000t" end="12355000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">开火</p>
<p begin="12486500000t" end="12507900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">我要…死了吗…</p>
<p begin="12516600000t" end="12538200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="12538200000t" end="12556700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">我对你…</p>
<p begin="12621600000t" end="12651200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">莉迪娅 辛苦你了</p>
<p begin="12651200000t" end="12674700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">回到我的灵魂之中吧</p>
<p begin="12677800000t" end="12692100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">遵命 我的王</p>
<p begin="12827000000t" end="12840100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="12851500000t" end="12879900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">哎呀 亚德果然厉害</p>
<p begin="12895200000t" end="12911100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">那么 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="12913900000t" end="12940200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">你还愿意继续跟我做朋友吗</p>
<p begin="12945500000t" end="12961500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">肯定愿意啊</p>
<p begin="12961500000t" end="12983500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">今后也请你多关照了 亚德</p>
<p begin="12999500000t" end="13007700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">好</p>
<p begin="13013600000t" end="13032800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">好了 赶紧回去吧</p>
<p begin="13037000000t" end="13063500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">金妮小姐应该为我们做好晚饭了</p>
<p begin="13088500000t" end="13108900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">我在想什么啊</p>
<p begin="13111900000t" end="13146600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">亚德知道了我的秘密 但还是把我当作朋友</p>
<p begin="13164200000t" end="13187400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">我必须…变强</p>
<p begin="13211900000t" end="13243700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">我要比谁都强 站到亚德身边</p>
<p begin="13251900000t" end="13269200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">只要这样 就一定能…</p>
<p begin="13430700000t" end="13509000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">超乎想像的未来正等待你发现</p>
<p begin="13509000000t" end="13573400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">打开大门的钥匙就在心中</p>
<p begin="13628100000t" end="13697400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">只要伸出你的手</p>
<p begin="13697400000t" end="13744500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">连未来都能改变</p>
<p begin="13744500000t" end="13815100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">冲动 渴望 重新开始</p>
<p begin="13822100000t" end="13868900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">若是转世重生 不要心存畏惧</p>
<p begin="13868900000t" end="13910600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">向甜美的过去告别</p>
<p begin="13914600000t" end="13961400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">在这日渐昏暗的世界</p>
<p begin="13961400000t" end="13993900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">随波逐流所无法掌握的自由</p>
<p begin="13993900000t" end="14046900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">去追求它吧</p>
<p begin="14051600000t" end="14083100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">舍弃孤独的强大</p>
<p begin="14085200000t" end="14120400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">追求相互理解的温暖</p>
<p begin="14120400000t" end="14154800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">将找到的那道光</p>
<p begin="14154800000t" end="14192400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">轻抱在怀里前行吧</p>
